Package: causalsim
Title: Simulation-Ready Causal Data Generating Processes
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Chayce", "Reed", , "code.jcr@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = ""))
Description: Construct, simulate, and evaluate causal data generating processes
    (DGPs) with known ground truth. Designed for benchmarking causal estimators,
    stress-testing assumption violations, and building reproducible teaching
    examples. Variable roles (confounder, instrument, mediator, effect modifier)
    and assumption violations (unmeasured confounding, positivity, effect
    heterogeneity) are first-class concepts in the API.
